{"data":{"actions":[{"callId":"chatcmpl-tool-ad2c77602b4bfe35","input":{"filename":"agent_fleet_router_action_report.md","title":"Prioritized Action Report – Agent Fleet Router","markdown":"# Prioritized Action Report – Agent Fleet Router\n\n**Context**\n- Dossier loaded for Agent 50‑fleet‑router (Operations). \n- Record analysis (limit 10) identified 3 key items with combined risk = 16 and opportunity = 11.4.\n\n## Top Records & Scores\n| ID | Title | Status | Impact | Risk | Opportunity | Score (Risk / Opp) |\n|----|-------|--------|--------|------|-------------|--------------------|\n| **50‑A** | Agent fleet router priority case | urgent | 57,850 | 2 | 7 | 6 / 7 |\n| **50‑C** | Agent fleet router blocked follow‑up | blocked | 28,550 | 5 | 2.9 | 7 / 2.9 |\n| **50‑B** | Agent fleet router routine queue item | in_review | 14,650 | 3 | 1.5 | 3 / 1.5 |\n\n## Prioritized Actions (under 500 words)\n\n### 1️⃣ Address **Urgent** record 50‑A\n- **Goal:** Resolve the highest‑impact open item (impact ≈ 58 k) that directly affects routing accuracy.\n- **Actions:**\n  1. Verify current routing rules against the **operating‑playbook** (skill `operating-playbook`).\n  2. Run a quick simulation of the routing pipeline to confirm the failure mode.\n  3. Deploy a hot‑fix or configuration tweak, then monitor for regressions.\n- **Owner:** Operations Lead, with support from the Routing Engineering team.\n- **Timeline:** Immediate – within the next 4 hours.\n\n### 2️⃣ Unblock **Blocked** record 50‑C\n- **Goal:** Remove cross‑functional blockers that prevent progress on a medium‑impact (≈ 28 k) item.\n- **Assumptions:** The block is due to pending dependencies from the Data Team.\n- **Actions:**\n  1. Convene a 30‑minute sync with Data and Ops leads to clarify required artefacts.\n  2. Document a temporary workaround to keep routing functional while dependencies are resolved.\n  3. Escalate to senior management if the dependency cannot be resolved within 24 hours.\n- **Owner:** Ops Coordinator.\n- **Timeline:** Resolve blockers within 1 day.\n\n### 3️⃣ Review **In‑Review** record 50‑B\n- **Goal:** Validate routine queue items and capture lessons for future triage.\n- **Actions:**\n  1. Conduct a lightweight peer‑review of the record’s impact assessment.\n  2. Update the routing playbook with any new best‑practice notes.\n  3. Archive the record once approved.\n- **Owner:** Junior Ops Analyst.\n- **Timeline:** Complete within 2 days.\n\n## Assumptions & Uncertainties\n- The risk/impact numbers provided by `analyze_records` are up‑to‑date.\n- No hidden dependencies beyond those identified for record 50‑C.\n- The operating‑playbook skill is accessible for step‑1 verification.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. **Trigger** the actions above using the appropriate specialized agents (e.g., `operating-playbook` for step 1).\n2. **Monitor** KPI – routing error rate, turnaround time, and risk reduction.\n3. **Report** status updates at end‑of‑day for items 50‑A and 50‑C.\n\n*Prepared by Agent 50‑fleet‑router (Operations) – routed for execution.*"},"kind":"tool-call","toolName":"write_report"}],"sequence":0,"stepIndex":3,"turnId":"turn_0"},"type":"actions.requested","meta":{"at":"2026-06-18T15:34:31.777Z"}}
